@startuml sequence_diagram_training
!theme plain
skinparam backgroundColor #FEFEFE
skinparam sequenceMessageAlign center

title Sequence Diagram Training Model Random Forest\nSistem Prediksi Penyebaran DBD

actor "Petugas" as User
participant "Halaman\nTraining" as Page
participant "Controller\nTraining" as Controller
participant "Python API\n(Flask)" as API
participant "Random Forest\nModel" as Model
database "Database" as DB

User -> Page : Buka menu Training Model
activate Page

Page --> User : Tampilkan form konfigurasi

User -> Page : Atur parameter\n(n_estimators, max_depth, test_size)
User -> Page : Klik tombol Mulai Training

Page -> Controller : Submit parameter training
activate Controller

Controller -> API : POST /train\n{n_estimators, max_depth, test_size}
activate API

API -> API : Load data dari Excel
API -> API : Preprocessing data\n(cleaning, encoding)
API -> API : Split data\n(training & testing)

API -> Model : Inisialisasi RandomForestClassifier
activate Model

Model -> Model : fit(X_train, y_train)
Model -> Model : predict(X_test)
Model -> Model : Calculate metrics\n(accuracy, precision, recall, f1)
Model -> Model : Calculate feature importance

Model --> API : Return trained model
deactivate Model

API -> API : Save model to file\n(random_forest_model.pkl)

API -> DB : INSERT INTO model_evaluasi\n(metrics, confusion_matrix)
activate DB
DB --> API : Success
deactivate DB

API --> Controller : Response\n{status, metrics, feature_importance}
deactivate API

Controller --> Page : Kirim hasil training
Page --> User : Tampilkan hasil evaluasi\n(Accuracy, Precision, Recall, F1)

deactivate Controller
deactivate Page

@enduml
